<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ExamMaster</title>
    <style>
      /* General Reset and Fonts */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      /* Headings */
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        color: #222;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: #444;
      }

      /* Paragraph Styling */
      p {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      /* Indented instructions */
      .ch {
        margin-left: 25px;
        color: #444;
      }

      .chch {
        margin-left: 50px;
        color: #555;
      }

      /* Consent checkbox row */
      #consent {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        margin-left: 25px;
      }

      #consent input[type="checkbox"] {
        width: 18px;
        height: 18px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .imp {
        color: red;
      }

      #consent p {
        margin: 0 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #222;
      }

      /* Start Test Button Section */
      #strt {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }

      #strt button {
        padding: 12px 20px;
        width: 180px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
        background-color: #0077cc;
        color: #fff;
        font-family: monospace;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      }

      #strt button:hover {
        background-color: #005fa3;
        transform: scale(1.03);
      }

      #strt button:active {
        transform: scale(0.98);
        background-color: #004a80;
      }

      form {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }

      form button {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2c3e50);
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      form button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      input:checked {
        display: none;
      }

      label {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 90%;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        margin: 8px 0;
        border: 2px solid transparent;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 500;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
      }

      input:checked + label,
      input:checked + label {
        border: 2px solid #8b5cf6;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
        color: #4c1d95;
      }

      /* for tick */
      input:checked + label::before,
      input:checked + label::before {
        content: "✓";
        position: absolute;
        left: -30px;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
        height: 20px;
        width: 20px;
        background-color: #8b5cf6;
        color: white;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 20px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>JEE Advanced Mock Test</h1>
    <h2>General Instructions:</h2>
    <p>
      1. The timer at the top of the screen will show the remaining time. The
      exam will automatically end when the time is over.
    </p>
    <p>
      2. The question palette on the right side will show the status of each
      question.
    </p>
    <p>3. <b>Navigating Between Questions:</b></p>
    <p class="ch">
      • Click on a question number in the palette to go to that question
      directly.
    </p>
    <p class="ch">
      • Use the “Next” and “Previous” buttons to navigate sequentially.
    </p>
    <p class="ch">• Click “Clear” to remove your selected response.</p>
    <p class="ch">
      • Clicking an option will automatically save your response.
    </p>

    <p>4. <b>Answering Questions:</b></p>
    <p class="ch"><b>Single Correct Type</b></p>
    <p class="chch">
      • Click on the option to select it. Only one option can be selected.
    </p>
    <p class="chch">• Click “Clear” to deselect your choice.</p>
    <p class="chch">
      • You can change your answer by clicking a different option.
    </p>

    <p class="ch"><b>Multiple Correct Type</b></p>
    <p class="chch">• Click on one or more options to select them.</p>
    <p class="chch">• Click again on an option to deselect it.</p>

    <p class="ch"><b>Numerical Type</b></p>
    <p class="chch">• Enter your answer using the keyboard.</p>
    <p class="chch">• Use the “Clear” button to erase your input.</p>

    <p>
      <b class="imp"
        >5. Please read all instructions carefully before each question.</b
      >
    </p>

    <div id="consent">
      <input type="checkbox" name="consent" id="consent-checkbox" />
      <label for="consent-checkbox"
        >I have read and understood all the instructions.</label
      >
    </div>

    <div id="strt">
      <button>START TEST</button>
    </div>
    <form method="get" action="/users/<%= user_id %>">
      <button>GO TO HOMEPAGE</button>
    </form>
  </body>
</html>
